                       AcceptanceInformation acceptanceInfo,
                       int ttbid,
                       int repid,
                       java.lang.String serial,

                       java.lang.String fancyName,

                       java.lang.String brand_name,
                       java.lang.String phone_number,
                       java.lang.String email,
                       java.lang.String date,
                       java.lang.String applicantName,
                       java.lang.String alcoholType,
                       java.lang.String alcoholContent)
        Creates an instance of Application Data.
        Parameters:
        formID - ID number of the form.
        acceptanceInfo - Information regarding the acceptance of the application; see the AcceptanceInformation class for more details.
        ttbid - ID generated by the TTB for tracking.
        repid - Representative ID.
        serial - Serial number for the application.
        address - Manufacturer's address.
        fancyName - Fanciful name of the alcohol.
        formula - Formula for the alcohol.
        permit_no - Number of the permit.
        infoOnBottle - String representing any additional info on the bottle.
        source_of_product - Location from which the product originated.
        type_of_product - Alcohol type.
        brand_name - Brand name of the alcohol.
        phone_number - Phone number for the manufacturer.
        email - Manufacturer's email address.
        date - Date of application.
        applicantName - Name of the applicant.
        alcoholType - Type of alcohol.
        alcoholContent - Alcohol content metric.
